Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.99,0:24:04.95,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2\an7}勉強露出寂寞的微笑
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.53,0:24:19.69,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2\an7}十字路口 信號燈 遠處的汽笛
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.86,0:24:26.72,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2\an7}陌生人的歡笑聲
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.87,0:24:34.73,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2\an7}今天一個人走在熟悉的街上
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.77,0:24:38.76,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2\an7}卻莫名覺得
Dialogue: 0,0:24:38.89,0:24:44.64,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2\an7}自己有些渺小
Dialogue: 0,0:24:45.92,0:24:49.78,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2\an7}「那麼再見吧」我揮手說道
Dialogue: 0,0:24:49.87,0:24:54.52,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2\an7}擠出寂寞的笑臉
Dialogue: 0,0:24:54.96,0:25:01.18,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2\an7}其實還想聊得更多
Dialogue: 0,0:25:01.30,0:25:05.18,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2\an7}「那麼再見吧」這句話
Dialogue: 0,0:25:05.28,0:25:09.86,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2\an7}還能再見的謊話
Dialogue: 0,0:25:10.20,0:25:15.85,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2\an7}帶著如同既往的笑臉說道
Dialogue: 0,0:25:15.96,0:25:19.17,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2\an7}「明天再見」
